co.cask.coopr.store.entity
Interface EntityStoreView

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseEntityStoreView, BaseSQLEntityStoreView, SQLAdminEntityStoreView, SQLUserEntityStoreView
public interface EntityStoreView

A view of the entity store for adding, modifying, retrieving, and deleting entities that are accessible by a tenant admin user. TODO: introduce concept of owner or group acls for these entities
